OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBanks pledge more          
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fprotection as mortgage     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Frates soar                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Banks and building societies will offer
OL,6, more flexibility to struggling         
OL,7, mortgage-holders as rates soar.        
OL,9,FThe move comes after bank bosses met   
OL,10,Fthe chancellor, Jeremy Hunt, in Downing
OL,11,FStreet on Friday.                      
OL,13,FBorrowers will be able to make a       
OL,14,Ftemporary change to their mortgage     
OL,15,Fterms, then will be able to return to  
OL,16,Ftheir original deal within six months. 
OL,18,FThis would allow some to have lower    
OL,19,Frepayments for a short time, by just   
OL,20,Fpaying the interest on the home loan.  
